profile:
Quite simply we exist to serve folks that want to maintain their independence and comfort of owning their home while having the peace of mind that your home maintenance, repairs and other personal services are in good hands with a reputable & caring service provider. 

Our services provide peace of mind to elderly home owners and their families as well as others that would like, or need assistance in the care & upkeep of their homes at reasonable rates.
